name: Hand-dyed dress, me&m spring / summer 2013
description:
Poplin soft cooling hand-dyed dress.
Wings-like detail at the back of the dress, waist string.
Shorter at the front, longer back side.
Poplin is lovely&shiny when ironed, nice&rugged-looking when worn without ironing.
Material: 80% cotton, 20% PES.
Sizing: 34 / 36 / 38 / 40.
Lenght is a matter of consultation.

name: Dress with hand crochet detail, me&m spring / summer 2013
description:
Atypical cut, hand crocheted detail at the back, soft lovely non-creasing lightweight satin.
Leaf shape lower front.
To be worn with or without waist string.
Material: 100% PES.
Sizing: 34 / 36 / 38 / 40.
Lenght is a matter of consultation.

name: Mint dress, me&m spring / summer 2013
description:
Lightweight lovely soft chiffon dress.
Frilling detail at the front, leather string tied at the back.
Material: 100% PES.
Sizing: 34 / 36 / 38 / 40.

name: Hand crochet shorts, me&m, spring / summer 2013
description:
Lovely summery surfy shorts, ideal over swimsuit or beige-colored underwear. Adds a detail under a short dress.
Custom design and hand crochet.
Material: 100% cotton
Sizes: 34 / 36 / 38 / 40

name: Assymetrical lace dress, me&m spring / summer 2013
description:
